- Mise checked
- Sauces hot
- Expo calls: "Doors in three"

@plane z=1 label="6:04 First Wave"
# 6:04 PM - First Wave

```
TICKET RAIL

  12  14  18
 [2] [4] [3] covers

GRILL: 2 steaks
SAUTE: 3 pastas
FRY:   4 fries
PASS:  garnish ready
